mployees who reside in broward county decreased before the announcement of the final headquarters site ryder considered some locations in miramar in broward county in  shoma development corp began demolishing the former ryder headquarters in doral replacing it with the park square at doral development ryder also has a shared services center in alpharetta ga that employs over  people and provides support to all fms operations locationsedit headquartered in miami ryder has satellite locations in  us states and also in mexico canada singapore china and the united kingdom criticismedit in december  the nonpartisan organization public campaign criticized ryder for spending  million on lobbying and not paying any taxes during – instead getting  million in tax rebates despite making a profit of  million referencesedit notes  ryder about usleadership retrieved july     httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpdlgetjjqowcloudfrontnetcikebfbddfedfpdf  a b c ryder history ryder system inc retrieved august     ryder media fact sheet ryder system inc retrieved august     ryder system inc google finance retrieved april     ryder system inc  form k edgar online retrieved april     ryder system inc company profile reuters retrieved august     ryder system inc company history funding universe retrieved may     a b c  annual report  business wire  ryder acquires portfolio of bit leasing  about ryder  ryder completes acquisition of the scully companies inc  ryder acquires big hollandbased warehouser with  employees nationwide  highbeamcom  contact us ryder retrieved on january    a b tamen joan fleischer ryder headquarters to be located near broward county fla border south florida sunsentinel december   retrieved on january    contact ryder ryder february   retrieved on january    urban living miami herald august   c busines