hez ceo art garcia cfo services fleet management supply chain management dedicated carrier cargo truck rental revenue us billion  operating income us million  net income us million  total assets us billion  total equity us billion  number of employees   website rydercom footnotes  references  a  ryder ford e a ryder daf lf truck in the united kingdom a ryder freightliner sprinter truck in the united states a ryder ford transit van in the united kingdom a isuzu nseries ryder system inc or ryder is an americanbased provider of transportation and supply chain management products and is especially known for its fleet of rental trucks ryder specializes in fleet management supply chain management and dedicated contracted carriage ryder operates in north america the united kingdom and asia it has its headquarters in suburban miami florida within miamidade county contents  history  business  fleet management  supply chain  dedicated contract carriage  rental trucks  headquarters  locations  criticism  references  external links historyedit this section needs expansion you can help by adding to it january  ryder was founded in miami florida in  by james ryder as a concrete hauling company with one truck a  model a ford within a few yearswhen the business expanded to leasing trucks to other companies this led to ryder changing its focus from distribution to leasing by  ryders truck fleet had increased to  ryder bought great southern trucking company in  in  ryder system inc was formed to combine great southern and ryder truck rental ryder system went public in  by the s and s ryder had expanded into the distribution and supply chain markets james a ryder founder and chairman retired in  in  ryder acquired three regional competitors pollock lily transportation and gator leasing businessedit ryder divides its business into three segments fleet management solutions supply chain solutions and dedicated contract carriage as of  the total company revenue was  billion earnings befor