his arm of the business does contractbased fullservice leasing contract maintenance commercial rental and fleet support services under fullservice leasing ryder owns and maintains the trucks and the customer decides where they go in contract maintenance ryder just takes care of the trucks commercial rentals are the white ryder trucks which the contract customers can rent on a temporary basis ryder grew its north american rental fleet to nearly  vehicles in  and  raising the percentage of model year  or newer vehicles in the fleet to more than  percent support services consist of insurance vehicle permits and fuel in april  ryder bought bit leasing from hayward california also in  it acquired the full service leasing and rental business of carmenita leasing inc located in santa fe springs california and the full service lease contract maintenance commercial rental and dedicated contract carriage business the scully companies inc based in fontana california supply chainedit ryder supply chain operations accounted for  of its revenue for a total of  billion profit of  million was  of the total this business consists of management of a customers supply chain ryder managed over  square feet  m of warehouse space on december   in december  ryder bought tlc a supply chain services company based in holland michigan dedicated contract carriageedit ryder dedicated contract carriage accounted for  of its revenue for a total of  billion profit of  million was  of the total this arm of the business conducts both leasing and supply chain management in  ryder launched a new name and identity for this program called ryder dedicated rental trucksedit ryder launched a consumer truckrental operation in  with  trucks and vans these were the yellow trucks known as oneways and available for the public to rent from filling stations and other automotiveservice locations in june  ryder decided to focus on commercial truck rental and leasing and exited the oneway business arena which it sold to budget truck rental the white ryder trucks seen on highways today are available to the general public looking to move locally returning the truck to the original pickup location businesses and companies that have a contractual agreement with ryder headquartersedit ryders headquarters are located in an unincorporated area in northwest miamidade county florida near the miami dadecounty broward county boundary line previously ryder had its headquarters in doral florida in  after taking a yearlong study of  potential headquarters sites in south florida ryder announced that it would move its headquarters to another location in northwest miamidade county the commute times of around  employees who reside in broward county decreased before the announcement of the final headquarters site ryder considered some locations in miramar in broward county in  shoma development corp began demolishing the former ryder headquarters in doral replacing it with the park square at doral development ryder also has a shared services center in alpharetta ga that employs over  people and provides support to all fms operations locationsedit headquartered in miami ryder has satellite locations in  us states and also in mexico canada singapore china and the united kingdom criticismedit in december  the nonpartisan organization public campaign criticized ryder for spending  million on lobbying and not paying any taxes during – instead getting  million in tax rebates despite making a profit of  million referencesedit notes  ryder about usleadership retrieved july     httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpsfinanceyahoocomquoterfinancialspr  httpdlgetjjqowcloudfrontnetcikebfbddfedfpdf  a b c ryder history ryder system inc retrieved august     ryder media fact sheet ryder system inc retrieved august     ryder system inc google finance retrieved april     ryder system inc  f