ges in accounting rules assumptions and accruals impact of actual insurance claim and settlement activity ÿ compared to historical loss development factors used to project future development lower than expected operating performance in our fms europe ÿ reporting unit could affect key assumptions used in our annual goodwill impairment test and result in impairment • other risks detailed from time to time in our sec filings including our  annual report on form k new risk factors emerge from time to time and it is not possible for management to predict all such risk factors or to assess the impact of such risk factors on our business as a result no assurance can be given as to our future results or achievements you should not place undue reliance on the forwardlooking statements contained herein which speak only as of the date of this quarterly report we do not intend or assume any obligation to update or revise any forwardlooking statements contained in this quarterly report whether as a result of new information future events or otherwise   edgar online source glimpses  latest news on ryder system inc  ryder system  managements discussion and analysis of financial condition and r  ryder system inc nyse  r reported earnings of  per share beating walls  ryder system inc nyse  r files an k results of operations and financial c  ryder system inc  results of operations and financial condition regulation fd   ryder system inc  investor network ryder system inc to host earnings call  ryder system  beats street q forecasts  ryder system  reports second quarter  results ryder system inc  halfyearly earnings release  ryder system  increases quarterly cash dividend  ryder system  introduces new maintenance offering on preowned vehicles more news news from seekingalpha  ryder system r q  results  earnings call transcript  ryder beats by  beats on revenue  notable earnings before wednesdays open   dividend increases  july    ryder declares  dividend traderscom marketsnewsanalysis